summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 4388 for the improvement of Harbor Avenue Southwest, from West Spokane Street to north line of West Florida Street on the east; by paving, and otherwise improving the same, under Ordinance No. 51908, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
